/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4260fa5311b6e5b0bd763dd439fb02808fb71091","tid":461462,"uid":25028,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:16:29.000Z","msg":"屌泡狗=祟日撚 d泡狗真係好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be9afc3e263d25e672164aca22f92d776d830cf","tid":461462,"uid":41238,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"通常會話韓燒係食醃料嘅人一定係食開港式韓燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實韓國根本係好少用醃料去整燒肉 同日燒一樣鐘意原汁原味 香港啲韓燒有醃肉只係為左貼近返香港人嘅重口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5d9083288a23e8514e9bc1a1369e6252d18881","tid":461462,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港嘅所謂'韓燒' 真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n利申先: 未去過韓國食韓燒，亦未去過日本食日燒，我只係分享下在澳洲見到嘅韓燒<br />\n<br />\n韓國人開嘅韓燒絕大多數都係炭燒，用GAS燒嘅基本都唔係韓國人開 (可能係華人)。<br />\n<br />\n肉方面，餐牌上只有少於三份一係醃肉，其他的都係無醃過的。<br />\n食法方面，韓國人會建議配上生菜 (西生菜，唔係香港食開一個波嗰種)、少量白飯、燒肉、醬汁、泡菜 (我自己就唔會加) 、炒過嘅洋蔥，包住一齊食，真係會好食好多<br />\n<br />\n如果有韓國紫菜，可以加埋入去或代替生菜，味道更佳。<br />\n<br />\n香港嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個d叫唐生菜呀小朋友 多d去買餸啦"},{"pid":"efffcf98ca28a124b6c3f86ca0fc2aaa4cca8683","tid":461462,"uid":9387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:28:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有幾多傻仔真係食過韓燒？唔係漢陽_個d呃人野</blockquote><br />\n班崇日撚分分鐘連高級日燒都未食過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最多咪盛八level扮食家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到高級韓燒就唔係餵狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高級韓燒係咪餵狗我就唔知<br />\n我淨